{"tid":1554235,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"VVD同意續約6年　薪酬連A山一半都冇","createTime":"2019-09-09T01:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T04:44:55.000Z","uid":103207,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1e492feea4916b4b87885212adb863c1e52834df","tid":1554235,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:44:56.000Z","msg":"英國《鏡報》爆料，<span style=\"color: red;\">利物浦中堅華基爾雲迪積克(VVD)已經同意續約6年，至2025年，週薪由現時12.5萬鎊，大幅增加至20萬鎊</span>，但相比起阿歷<span style=\"color: red;\">斯山齊士50萬鎊週薪，呢位荷蘭國腳待遇其實相當低</span>。<br />\n<br />\n28歲嘅華基爾雲迪積克上年由修咸頓，加盟利物浦之後，表現出頂級中堅實力，早前更力壓兩大球王美斯同C朗，成為今年歐洲最佳球員，好可能會贏埋世界足球先生。因此，有傳VVD可能會要求天價人工續約，但結果只係20萬鎊，以佢<span style=\"color: red;\">今時今日嘅級數，簡直係「低薪一族」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n而且華基爾<span style=\"color: red;\">雲迪積克續約6年，意味約滿時已經34歲，決心將球員最黃金時間貢獻畀利物浦</span>，難怪被睇好將會成為紅軍下任隊長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9d79e064ade090cfd24dac3b7b82e18d5bdc01","tid":1554235,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:50:04.000Z","msg":"@牙蓋"},{"pid":"569efc92d61d1b5bd2b01bcff5a5979b391e969e","tid":1554235,"uid":133787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"續約唔代表長留，例子有古天奴"},{"pid":"c40316bd3953327fb3bb4c8e521df8e6b063ddfe","tid":1554235,"uid":11381,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:53:51.000Z","msg":"75m追隻契弟小醜，真係痢狗先做到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/538208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/538208</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a15209a92754706fa490c78610b9c18b69e920bd","tid":1554235,"uid":30768,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:53:54.000Z","msg":"0嘅一半都係0"},{"pid":"51fd1e169e2e70b6876ef391fd54f13fb0e92d4f","tid":1554235,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c9d79e064ade090cfd24dac3b7b82e18d5bdc01","tid":1554235,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-0